
'''OpenStreetMap''' ( '''OSM''' ) ndi [[Virtual community|polojekiti yogwirizana yopanga]] [[Map|mapu]] okonzedwanso [[Free content|omasuka]] a dziko lapansi.  M'malo mwa mapepala okhaokha, [[Geodata|deta yomwe]] imapangidwa ndi polojekitiyi imatengedwa kuti ndiyo yaikulu yomwe imayambira.  Zolengedwa ndi kukula kwa OSM zakhala zikulimbikitsidwa ndi zoletsa kugwiritsa ntchito kapena kupezeka kwa mapu kumudzi konse, komanso kubwera kwa zipangizo zamakono zotetezera [[Satellite navigation|satana]] .  OSM imatengedwa ngati chitsanzo chodziwika cha [[Volunteered geographic information|kudzipereka kwadzidzidzi]] . 

Cholengedwa ndi [[Steve Coast]] ku UK mu 2004, chinauziridwa ndi kupambana kwa Wikipedia ndi malo omwe [[Vendor lock-in|ali ndi]] mapu [[Vendor lock-in|enieni]] ku UK ndi kwina kulikonse.  Kuyambira ntha≈µi imeneyo, yakula kwa anthu oposa 2 miliyoni olemba ntchito,  omwe angathe kusonkhanitsa deta pogwiritsa ntchito kufufuza, zipangizo za [[GPS]] , [[Aerial photography|kujambula zam'lengalenga]] , ndi zina zowonjezera.  Izi [[Crowdsourcing|crowdsourced]] deta ndiye limapanga pansi [[Open Database License|Open Nawonso achichepere License]] .  Malowa amathandizidwa ndi [[OpenStreetMap Foundation]] , bungwe lopanda phindu lolembetsedwa ku England ndi Wales. 

Deta yochokera ku OSM imapezeka kuti igwiritsidwe ntchito pazinthu zonse, monga momwe amagwiritsira ntchito [[Facebook]] , [[Craigslist]] , [[OsmAnd]] , [[Geocaching]] , [[MapQuest]] Open, [[JMP (statistical software)|JMP mapulogalamu]] , ndi Ma [[Foursquare]] kuti agwirizane ndi [[Google Maps]] , ndi maudindo ena odabwitsa monga kusintha deta yosasinthika yomwe ilipo ndi GPS olandila. Dongosolo la OpenStreetMap lapindula poyerekeza ndi zomwe zilipo, ngakhale mu 2009 khalidwe lachidziwitso linasiyanasiyana padziko lonse lapansi.  

